title: The J&J Team - JJ Holistic Nutritional Therapy
description: Our team has a commendable pool of knowledge concerning many foods, diets, foodprotocols, and nutritional supplements. Therefore, we use this knowledge in devising a diet and nutrient plan suitable for individual patients. We use a natural and differentapproach to each individual.
